# Task Dashboard

A modern, responsive Task Manager Dashboard built with React and Tailwind CSS.  
Designed to showcase clean code, component-based architecture, and practical web app functionality.

## Features
- Add, delete, and mark tasks as completed
- Filter tasks by status (All / Active / Completed)
- Responsive design for mobile and desktop
- Persistent data using LocalStorage

## Tech Stack
- React 18
- Tailwind CSS
- Vite for fast build tooling

